# SwiftSpend Financial – Phishing Kit Investigation

## Objective

The goal of this project was to investigate a phishing campaign targeting employees at **SwiftSpend Financial** in a TryHackMe phishing analysis room.

The investigation focused on analyzing suspicious emails, identifying phishing URLs, reviewing a credential harvesting page, retrieving an exposed phishing kit, using threat intelligence tools, and extracting indicators of compromise to support SOC triage and response.

Sensitive victim information, submitted passwords, and challenge flag values have been redacted to follow responsible reporting practices.

