## Example Detection Queries

### Search for Emails from the Suspicious Sender

```spl
index=email sender="Accounts.Payable@groupmarketingonline.icu"
```

### Search for DNS Queries to the Phishing Domain

```spl
index=dns query="kennaroads.buzz"
```

### Search for Proxy Traffic to the Phishing Domain

```spl
index=proxy url_domain="kennaroads.buzz"
```

### Search for Downloads of the Phishing Kit Archive

```spl
index=proxy uri_path="*/Update365.zip"
```

### Search for Access to the Exposed Directory

```spl
index=proxy url="*kennaroads.buzz/data*"
```

### Search for Microsoft Login Impersonation Activity

```spl
index=proxy url="*kennaroads.buzz*" AND (uri_path="*/login*" OR uri_path="*/data*")
```

